Race.SpecificTitle: Justice of the Peace -- Justice of the Peace District 3
PW- Police Jury -- 4 Mills - Police Jury - 10 Years
Race.SummaryText:
Parishwide Proposition
(Millage)

Summary:  10 year, 4 mills property tax to acquire, improve, maintain, operate and support facilities, equipment, programs and services for senior citizens of Concordia Parish, including providing funding for facilities, equipment, programs and services provided by the Concordia Parish Council on Aging.
Race.FullText: Shall the Parish of Concordia, State of Louisiana (the "Parish"), levy a special tax of four (4) mills on all the property subject to taxation within the Parish (an estimated $440,000 reasonably expected at this time to be collected from the levy of the tax for an entire year) for a period of ten (10) years, beginning with the year 2009 and ending with the year 2018, to acquire, improve, maintain, operate and support facilities, equipment, programs and services for senior citizens of the Parish, including providing funding for facilities, equipment, programs and services provided by the Concordia Parish Council on Aging?
